title: Poorly Designed Teapot
description: Do you ever get the desire to drink a cup of tea while also potentially causing moderate to severe burns? If so, look no further, this teapot is the only one of its kind to deliver that outcome every time!

title: 1970's Lead-Based Paint
description: The 70's was a decade that contained some of the best music and films of the 20th Century. Now you too can relive that era of history with some of the lovely lead based, from our select pre-1978 vintage!

title: Insulin, that does work on Poor People
description: Isn't strange how nearly every president since Jimmy Carter has explicitly run on the promise of lowering the price of insulin and yet it never seems to happen? Well, we wanna keep it that way, so introducing a new formulation which specifically doesn't work unless you meet a six-figure income threshold.

title: Trip to The Elmer's Glue, Sticky Waterpark
description: They all told me a glue based waterpark was a foolish idea! 'It'll never work', they said. 'Can you even call it a waterpark if all the rides use glue' they asked? Well I did not yield to naysayers of this, or any other world. I WILL FACE GOD AND WALK BACKWARDS INTO HELL!

title: Meat Freshener
description: The ONLY air freshner marketed for specific use on raw meat.

title: 'Real' Snake Oil
description: Is it oil that's meant for snakes or an oil made from snakes? Unclear! Guess you'll just have to buy some in order to find out!

title: Friendship Scissor
description: Most scissors come in pairs so they can acomplish their designed purpose. But we at the ---- decided that in these devicive times was more important to try and bring folks together. To wit, the friendship scissor which only comes with half a scissor requiring you to go out and make friends with another person who purchased their own friendship scissor....or you can always just buy two.
